title: Clean & Clear Continuous Control Acne Cleanser,  5 oz  (141g)
description: Clean & Clear Continuous Control Acne Cleanser not only removes dirt and oil, it also features a porepenetrating technology that deposits acne medicine to help fight and help prevent breakouts long after you wash. Your skin is clean and becomes clearer with continued use.

title: Moroccan Oil Hair Treatment 3.4 Oz Bottle with Blue Box
description: Moroccanoil is an ultra-light formula which is absorbed by the hair instantly, resulting in a natural, silky finish and brilliant shine.
